Argos: Continues to point his guns at azure, hearing that Rodimus is outside he says " There is no Problems her is ther Azure, Were'nt you just leaving." as He spots Dragos taking off in the Distance and the rest of the fuzors taking off after Dragos. Argos Trirls his guns in his hands and states. " What is up with them, Oh wait I am part of them. Well I'll go find out what is going on. Oh and Azure you best not be here when I get back." At that Argos transforms into a Spider and takes off with great speed after the fuzors. 

OMWOS <o_mighty_wife_of_shinigami@...> wrote:OOC: All righty, bit confused here but trudging ahead

IC: Cheetor shrugged his shoulders, not sure if he should transform and 
be ready to fight and sat back on his haunches, watching the Maximal 
now Pred and some stranger. hHe looked up at the arrival of his leader.

"Big bo-...," the young Maximal trailed off as the familar nickname he 
had grown acustomed to calling his former leader. He dropped his head, 
before raising it and continuing. "I'm not sure Rodimus." 

OMWOS
